                <h1 class="account-header account-header-low-margin-top">Weird Endpoint: The tagline as a Resource?</h1>
                
                                    <p class="hidden-xs">
                        Course:
                        <a class="knp-color-black" href="resume"><em>Symfony RESTful API: Hypermedia, Links &amp; Bonuses (Course 5) Tutorial</em></a>                    </p>
