<p>But how should we pass the new <code>tagline</code> data? Normally, we send a json-encoded array
of fields. But this resource isn't a collection of fields: it's just <em>one</em> string.
There's nothing wrong with sending some JSON data up like before, but you could also
set the <code>body</code> to the plain-text <code>New Tag Line</code> itself:</p>
