</div>
</p>
<p>Literally: read the text from the request body and set that on the programmer.</p>
<p>Now, save: <code>$em = $this-&gt;getDoctrine()-&gt;getManager()</code>, <code>$em-&gt;persist($programmer)</code>
and <code>$em-&gt;flush()</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="16b03773d5">
