</p>
<p>Now, this is a good-looking, super-weird endpoint. Copy the test method name and try
it out:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">./vendor/bin/phpunit --filter testEditTagLine</div></code></pre>
<p>We're green! Next, let's look at a <em>weirder</em> endpoint.</p>

    
